text: Quijote TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in March 2006 and can be seen in the Sucre Municipality of the Zulia State of Venezuela on UHF channel 69. Jairo Almao and Jorge Barreto are the legal representatives of the foundation that owns this channel.
